        "description": "Get a single service connection. Secret is never returned — only hasSecret + secretPreview.\n\nCall via POST /api/v1/mcp with a JSON-RPC `tools/call` body. This path exists in the OpenAPI spec for tool discoverability only — direct POSTs to this URL return 405.",
